================================================================================
TUESDAY, DECEMBER 10, 2025 - PART 2
================================================================================

Tasks Completed:

1. USER PROFILE IMPLEMENTATION UNIFICATION
   - Replaced user profile implementation with admin profile implementation
   - Maintained usertemplate layout for student-specific styling
   - Unified functionality across both profiles:
     * Tab structure (My Details, Login)
     * Form fields (Basic Info, Parent Details, Login/Account)
     * Image cropper functionality with Cropper.js
     * Account deletion with email confirmation
     * Password management and change functionality
     * Profile photo upload with drag-and-drop support
     * All JavaScript functionality and event listeners

2. PROFILE UPDATE VALIDATION FIXES
   - Added missing validation rules for parent information fields:
     * parent_first_name (nullable|string|max:255)
     * parent_last_name (nullable|string|max:255)
     * parent_email (nullable|email)
     * parent_phone (nullable|string|max:20)
   - Updated UserController.updateProfile() validation rules
   - Added logging for validation errors for debugging

3. PROFILE PHOTO UPLOAD OPTIMIZATION
   - Identified and fixed file size issue (files were >10MB)
   - Optimized image cropping:
     * Reduced max dimensions from 4096x4096 to 800x800 pixels
     * Changed format from PNG to JPEG with 0.8 quality compression
     * Reduced file size from ~10MB to ~50-100KB
   - Updated validation rule to 5120 KB (5MB) max file size
   - Added GIF format support to validation rules
   - Improved error handling with detailed console logging
   - Added validation error messages displayed to users

4. ERROR HANDLING AND DEBUGGING
   - Enhanced saveProfileData() error handling
   - Added detailed error logging in browser console
   - Displays specific validation error messages to users
   - Logs validation errors to Laravel logs for server-side debugging

